    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're trapped in an abandoned hospital with one job: rescue your friend and get out alive. Explore the hospital, solve puzzles, and uncover keys hidden around the hospital to unlock your escape route. But stay alert—the hospital isn't as empty as it seems. An evil doctor prowls the halls, always hunting for the next patient to lock away. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314040/extras/c31374fc3ab789305cd15e44a5e43593.webp?t=1741849940\" width=293 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends to boost your chances of survival—there’s strength in numbers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314040/extras/557af33cc06a41fcaa759a08f2fea7fe.avif?t=1741849940\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314040/extras_big/557af33cc06a41fcaa759a08f2fea7fe.avif?t=1741849940 width=800 height=75 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you fall victim to the doctor, your mission isn't over. Assist your teammates using the hospital’s CCTV room to track danger and guide their escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314040/extras/7376f31ac6d7468a0bcc44df9cbbb319.webp?t=1741849940\" width=293 height=50 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay alert—the doctor patrols the hospital relentlessly, using sharp senses and clever tactics to hunt you down. Move quietly and carefully; he’s always watching, always waiting for a mistake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you rescue your friend, outsmart the relentless doctor, and escape the nightmare? Or will you become yet another permanent resident of the hospital’s forgotten halls?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The choice is yours.</p>",
